      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and represents the pinnacle of its model year. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its original factory luster with no scratches, dents, or chips of any kind. Inside, the cabin is pristine and smells like new, with the leather upholstery and trim showing zero signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been stored in a climate-controlled garage and meticulously maintained with a full service history. This is a collector-quality example that drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor.",
