      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable condition, mirroring its original showroom presentation in every discernible detail. Meticulously maintained and preserved to the highest standards, it offers a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing short of perfection. Every surface, mechanical component, and interior appointment reflects a commitment to excellence and uncompromising care.",
