    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve kept it tucked away and pampered it since day one\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one. Come take it for a spin, you're going to fall in love!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level 2011 Carrera S, a definitive example of the 997.2 chassis. This specimen features the 3.8L naturally aspirated flat-six equipped with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), eliminating the IMS concerns of predecessors. Power is delivered via a precise 6-speed longitudinal manual gearbox to a factory-optioned limited-slip differential. The vehicle is fitted with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), ensuring optimal damping rates and roll stiffness. Mechanical integrity is verified by a clean DME readout with zero over-revs in higher ranges. From the unblemished ceramic composite rotors to the factory-spec torque values on every suspension link, this vehicle remains in a state of mechanical stasis. A turnkey acquisition for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. No accidents. Clean title. Garage kept. Flawless interior.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade example that defies its age. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving the deep, mirror-like finish of its original factory paint, which has been further enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather upholstery shows no bolster wear or creasing and has been conditioned quarterly. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the seat heaters, functions with factory-new precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive service binder documenting every oil change and preventative inspection performed by certified technicians. There are no stone chips on the fascia, no curb rash on the alloy wheels, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean. This is a rare opportunity to own a time-capsule vehicle that has been loved rather than just driven.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
