      "description": "Hey everyone! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total gem! This car has been pampered since day one and is in truly stunning condition\u2014it seriously looks and drives like it just left the showroom. If you're looking for something that\u2019s been loved and kept in tip-top shape, this is the one for you. I'd love for it to go to a great new home, so come say hi and take a look!",
