    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a precision-calibrated VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip differential, ensuring linear power delivery and exceptional mechanical grip. This specific example boasts a documented service history including rod bearing replacement and proactive rear subframe reinforcement, addressing the chassis's known stress points. The exterior finish remains in showroom state with no evidence of clear coat failure or panel misalignment, while the interior leather maintains its original matte texture. A true turn-key specimen for the collector who demands mechanical perfection and high-revving performance.",
